{"tid":884871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾徵費唔攪垃圾分類  究竟主要目的係環保定掠水？","createTime":"2018-11-01T02:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T00:04:42.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b0278ddceeb1170af5cdc79567a14932b6e1ff53","tid":884871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd6499e66a1bdba319a48f84cffb865027df44d","tid":884871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:41:49.000Z","msg":"環保  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n掠水  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a231ab6ea2d39847d76bb22388a37ab739735c7c","tid":884871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e795acab76e456c9a2a32bb17741cb9d4666821","tid":884871,"uid":46527,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:54:45.000Z","msg":"假環保，真掠水"},{"pid":"46bca5465514c1ff54f4a4d5285aa17893736a9f","tid":884871,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"你唔覺得佢掠水，又點會主動減少垃圾"},{"pid":"1d4cf739bff3553e77521ca7dc3442db23de0f3e","tid":884871,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"46bca5465514c1ff54f4a4d5285aa17893736a9f","tid":884871,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"你唔覺得佢掠水，又點會主動減少垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:59:49.000Z","msg":"懲罰性收費"},{"pid":"58334918a71fdbde31c0697efc516095a72b8dfe","tid":884871,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾收費真係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  香港講環保真係曬鳩氣"},{"pid":"03d6d0afb8c9aa441ad95033ee4d1f13f11d52be","tid":884871,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:11:38.000Z","msg":"台北市垃圾徵費<br />\n<br />\n本市實施「隨袋徵收」垃圾費，<span style=\"color: red;\">市民丟棄一般垃圾，必須購買環保局規定的「專用垃圾袋」來裝垃圾。但是，市民將環保局指定垃圾中可回收的資源分類出來，可以免費送交清潔隊清運</span>，因此市民不但可以直接享受到「垃圾減量」及「資源回收」而少付垃圾費的好處，且間接貢獻地球的「環境保護」及「生態保育」，造福後代的子子孫孫。市民增加的不方便就是要特別去買「專用垃圾袋」及做「垃圾分類」的工作。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dep.gov.taipei/News_Content.aspx?n=9D5081C3BFCC977A&amp;s=FB47A528846715AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dep.gov.taipei%2FNews_Content.aspx%3Fn%3D9D5081C3BFCC977A%26s%3DFB47A528846715AA&d=b7DOn9OyI3Miq2JAdG7N8HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d0f52a23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dep.gov.taipei/News_Content.aspx?n=9D5081C3BFCC977A&amp;s=FB47A528846715AA</a><br />\n分類垃圾免費<br />\n一般垃圾才收費(未能分類)"},{"pid":"b88225abfe30e5adaf24b9f1df5ccc7bce1708bd","tid":884871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8733c94e2c222137b6a9c041f0a207f1f8bd20d","tid":884871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e438f0cd1ecf56dca1fcbd2284769fb2dcb49ac","tid":884871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a39691d2ace28593e185a4624922e1845fe8b7","tid":884871,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:13:28.000Z","msg":"後者。"},{"pid":"23a1ed55838527e22d5a5a8236c052bc0bd6b4ff","tid":884871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T23:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362aed9f0713431fb7571f096ef51b74e00fc20d","tid":884871,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:04:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾稅同煙草稅其實一樣，徵費嘅目標係希望徵唔到費，即係透過經濟壓力而非誘因逼使民眾改變行為，由食煙（要花錢俾稅）轉向戒煙（唔使錢）。<br />\n<br />\n同一道理，垃圾稅應該係希望逼使民眾由一桶專棄轉向細緻回收、源頭減廢，但政府到目前仍然無充足嘅回收配套，民眾根本無避開呢種稅項嘅逃生門，最後垃圾都係一樣咁掉，但市民開支就無故增加咗。"}]}